# DUOC UC Kiosk Application — Implementation Plan

Complete React + Vite self-service kiosk with virtual avatar "Leonor", state machine, Web Speech API STT, Claude API integration, accessible mode, and session management.

## Proposed Changes

### Scaffolding

#### [NEW] Project init via `npx create-vite`
Initialize React + Vite in existing directory, install dependencies.

#### [NEW] [.env.example](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/.env.example)
Template with `VITE_CLAUDE_API_KEY=tu_api_key_aqui`.

---

### Constants

#### [NEW] [videos.js](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/src/constants/videos.js)
Map of state → video path for all 11 `.mp4` files.

#### [NEW] [tramites.js](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/src/constants/tramites.js)
Array of 4 trámites (certificado alumno regular, horario académico, progreso académico, situación financiera) with id, name, description, simulated result string.

---

### State Machine

#### [NEW] [totemMachine.js](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/src/machines/totemMachine.js)
Pure JS state machine (no XState). States: `IDLE → WELCOME → LOGIN → MENU → CONFIRMING → EXECUTING → RESULT → GOODBYE`. Transition function `transition(state, event)` returns new state + context. Handles retry logic, asesor derivation, and `accionesExitosas` threshold.

---

### Services

#### [NEW] [claudeService.js](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/src/services/claudeService.js)
`mapVoiceToOption(transcript)` → calls Anthropic API via fetch with system prompt to map spoken text to option 0-4. Returns number or `null` on failure.

---

### Hooks

#### [NEW] [useSpeech.js](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/src/hooks/useSpeech.js)
Uses `webkitSpeechRecognition` / `SpeechRecognition`. Exposes `{ transcript, isListening, startListening, stopListening, resetTranscript }`.

#### [NEW] [useSession.js](file:///c:/Users/tania/OneDrive%20-%20Fundacion%20Instituto%20Profesional%20Duoc%20UC/Escritorio/avatar-duocuc/src/hooks/useSession.js)
Manages `accionesExitosas`, `reintentosBio`, `modoAccesible`, and 120s inactivity timer that resets on interaction.

